node.text: A quick ride off the shores of Miami is beautiful Bimini, an island I hold close to my heart. Filmed this three years ago & finally brought it to life. Leave your feedback in the comments! 🤙 This mystic, gorgeous & historical island has been loved by everyone from Ernest Hemingway to Martin Luther King Jr. For those who love tropical vibes, adventure, & culture - this island must go on your bucketlist! 🐬 Id love your support! Don’t forget to share this video, tag friends & like this post. Love you Grubfam! 🙏 Thanks for the assist on filming @znicolaou & as always, thank you for making my vision come to life, @jessyfiggsfilmsphotography ❗️ #TheGrubfather #Bimini #Bahamas #BiminiBliss

🦀 SOFT SHELL CRAB PASTA 🍝 @SEABAROFFICIAL is an incredible seafood restaurant and has these tasty delicacies available through the next week! 😋

💯 They will let you customize how it comes prepared but I suggest crowning them ontop of Sea Bar’s amazing creamy pink pasta! 

❗️Side note: The crabs were already ☠️ when it was cleaned in the beginning.

💪 2020 vs 2021 👉 180 vs 150! My fitness journey has been a complicated one as my relationship with food, as you all know, is an interesting one. I debated posting this because it’s not something I’m too open about… But I want to change that! ✔️ I can’t tell you how many times I get asked “how do you stay so small with all this food?!” and the fact is that it wasn’t always that way and it definitely comes down to a few things: 

1️⃣ Intermittent fasting! This is a MAJOR 🔑 

2️⃣ Eliminating sugar intake when I’m not shooting / taste testing - sometimes dipping into ketosis.

3️⃣ Putting in *meaningful* work at the gym, which my trainer @RVTFITNESS has been such a huge help with. 

4️⃣ Allowing myself to enjoy the foods I love, but doing so in moderation and with gratitude. 

5️⃣ When you want to give up, go deeper into it. Develop a beast mode mentality and hold yourself to the highest standard! 

❗️This page is undeniably a vessel of indulgent, GRUB-centric food. That will never change. But I think my duty as a public figure in the food space is to also provide some health conscious recipes, restaurant dishes + tips as well. So expect some of that in the coming weeks. 

💥 These past few months I’ve learned that health is such a beautiful achievement. Health doesn’t mean skinny either, it means feeling good at your core in both body + mind. ♥️ 

🏃‍♂️ As I’ve always said, The Grubfam aka YOU is like my family. We’ve built such a beautiful platform together. If I can provide even a spark of inspiration for you to embark on a fitness / health journey (while also giving you allll the cheat day recommendations) that would make my heart and spirit full. 

👀 Let me know what you think!

Much love,
Sal ✌️ #TheGrubfather

❗️SWEET TOAST RECIPE ✖️ Easy, delicious & relatively healthy! This one is good for a night time sweet tooth craving or a charged way to get your morning started. Full recipe below 👇 

1️⃣ Add 1 tablespoon of Kerry Gold butter, a sprinkle of pumpkin spice or cinnamon & a tablespoon of coconut sugar to a pan. Low heat until butter is melted. 

2️⃣ Add bread to pan and brown on both sides. 

3️⃣ In a bowl mix half a can of pure pumpkin purée, 2 tablespoons of peanut butter and a tablespoon of agave. Mix well. 

4️⃣ Coat toast in mixture, sprinkle more pumpkin spice / cinnamon + agave to the top. 

5️⃣ Add sliced banana and dollops of strawberry jam. 

6️⃣ DIG IN❗️

😉 This one is super simple and I promise it hits all the spots. ✔️ Follow me for more recipes, food + travel! #TheGrubfather #Recipes

🔥 PORTUGUESE COAL FIRED CHICKEN @CHURRASQUEIRABAIRRADA 😋 One of my favorite chickens in all of NY - watch til the end to find out why. 👀 

 🍗 This old world, rustic technique is a win every time - plus, it’s pretty damn healthy. It gets coated in their secret sauce and Portuguese sea salt through the cooking process. ✔️ This Portuguese restaurant is famous for their Franco de Churrasco and you MUST brush their homemade hot sauce all over it. Divine. 

👉 If you’re a MEAT LOVER consider this rodizio restaurant a must hit. More today on stories! Follow me for more food and travel. ♥️ #TheGrubfather #Mineola #LongIsland

🔥 SMOKED + DEEP FRIED CHEESE-BURGER @TEAMSMOKHAUS 🍔 Yes, you read that right! This BBQ joint just debuted this new burger which gets smoked for 30 minutes, deep fried for a beautiful crisp. 👉 Not to mention there are FIVE CHEESES atop this monster + SPICY MAYO. 🎯 

✖️ @TEAMSMOKHAUS is a BBQ restaurant in Garden City, Long Island. They’ve got some crazy creations - some of which I’ve created myself (try the ULTIMATE BBQ sandwich sometime too) 😉

❗️GRUB RECIPE: SPICY MAYO CHICKEN SALAD SANDWICH 🤙 I’m a HUGE fan of spicy mayo & I love chicken salad sandwiches, so I thought… why haven’t I had it together?! 🤔 Hitting you with the full recipe below. If you like a little heat, a little sweet & a lot of good flavor - this one is for you. ✔️ 

👉 RECIPE 👇 
1️⃣ Shred all the white meat out of a rotisserie chicken. Leave no skin. 
2️⃣ For spicy mayo, combine a small jar of mayo, sriracha to your tasting and a dollop of honey to balance it out. Mix well. 
3️⃣ Add your spicy mayo to chicken and beat until well blended. 
4️⃣ Add in CAYENNE, MUSTARD POWDER, GARLIC POWDER, SALT + PEPPER to taste into the salad. 
4️⃣ Coat two pieces of country white bread with mayo on one side and put on a nonstick griddle/pan. 
5️⃣ Quickly add 2-3 slices of cheddar cheese and steam until melted. Remove from grill. 
6️⃣ Layer thinly sliced vine tomatoes, chicken salad and shredded butter lettuce between bread. 
7️⃣ Cut down the middle and DIG IN 

🎯 I really enjoyed how this one came out. I am so not into celery in my chicken salad but if you are, go for it!
